data.description: Discover your dream retreat in the heart of Yosemite Lakes Park! Nestled on just over 5 acres, this 3 bedroom, 2 bath home offers an expansive 1,616 sq. ft. of comfortable living space. Be captivated by breathtaking views that stretch as far as the eye can see, creating a serene backdrop for everyday life. Perfect for a primary, vacation, or Airbnb home!Step inside and be welcomed by the inviting living room, adorned with vaulted ceilings that elevate the ambiance of your new home. The open-concept kitchen is a culinary enthusiast's delight, complete with brand-new double-pane windows that flood the space with natural light. Upgraded carpet throughout adds a touch of luxury to every bedroom of the home.Embrace the resort-like lifestyle that Yosemite Lakes Park offers to you. YLP offers a beautiful lake perfect for fishing, a golf course for leisurely rounds, and a charming restaurant and bar for social gatherings. The community also boasts private security, a clubhouse for relaxation, a refreshing swimming pool, tennis courts, and much more.Make this home yours and indulge in a lifestyle that merges natural beauty with modern comfort. Experience the stunning vistas and a wealth of amenities. Your perfect Yosemite Lakes Park haven awaits!Nestled in an ideal location,this home is just a 30 min. drive to the iconic Yosemite National Park, and a short 15 min. drive to Chuckchansi Gold Resort & Casino, providing entertainment and excitement at your doorstep.HOA $2,013.00 / year.
